on Cannon Street]]\n*[[Charing Cross railway station|London Charing Cross]]\n*[[Euston railway station|London Euston]]\n*[[Fenchurch Street railway station|London Fenchurch Street]]\n*[[London King's Cross railway station|London Kings Cross]]\n*[[Liverpool Street station|London Liverpool Street]]\n*[[Marylebone station|London Marylebone]]\n*[[London Paddington station|London Paddington]]\n*[[St Pancras railway station|London St Pancras International]]\n*[[London Victoria station|London Victoria]]\n*[[London Waterloo station|London Waterloo]]\n*[[London Waterloo East railway station|London Waterloo East]]\n*[[Moorgate station|Moorgate Underground]]\n*[[Old Street station|Old Street Underground]]\n*[[Stratford station|Stratford]]\n*[[Vauxhall station|Vauxhall]]\n*[[Surbiton station|Surbiton]]\n*[[Wimbledon station|Wimbledon]]\n*[[Richmond station (London)|Richmond]]\n}}\n\n===Roadways===\n\n====Footpaths====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[Capital Ring]]\n* [[South East London Green Chain|Green Chain]]\n* [[London Outer Orbital Path]]\n* [[Thames Path]]\n}}\n\n====Major roads====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[M1 motorway]]\n* [[M25 motorway]]\n* [[M3 motorway (Great Britain)|M3 motorway]]\n* [[M4 motorway]]\n* [[M11 motorway]]\n* [[A406 road|North Circular Road]] (A406)\n* [[South Circular Road, London|South Circular Road]] (A205)\n* The [[London Inner Ring Road]]\n}}\n\n====Roman roads====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[Ermine Street]]\n* [[Oxford Street]]\n* [[Watling Street]]\n}}\n\n====Streets and squares====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[Abbey Road, London|Abbey Road]]\n* [[Aldwych]]\n* [[Baker Street]]\n* [[Bayswater Road]]\n* [[Berkeley Square]]\n* [[Bond Street]]\n* [[New Bond Street]]\n* [[Brompton Road]]\n* [[Cannon Street]]\n* [[Charing Cross Road]]\n* [[Cheapside]]\n* [[Commercial Road]]\n* [[Connaught Square]]\n* [[Coventry Street]]\n* [[Downing Street]]\n* [[Edgware Road]]\n* [[Electric Avenue]]\n* [[Fleet Street]]\n* [[Gipsy Hill]]\