tral\n|}\n\n\u2020 = Outer London for statistics | * = Inner London for statistics\n\n===Sub-regions===\n*[[North London]] and [[South London]]: the division of London by the River Thames\n*[[West End of London]], [[Central London]], [[East End of London]] and the [[South Bank]]: sections of the historic urban core\n*[[London Docklands]]: the former docks and now a regeneration area\n*[[London Plan#Sub regions|London Plan sub-regions]]: North East, North, South East, South West, West\n*[[London postal district|Various postcode areas covering London]]\n*[[London fare zones|Public transport zones]]: [[Travelcard Zone 1|1]] (central London); [[Travelcard Zone 2|2]] (inner city); [[Travelcard Zone 3|3]] and [[Travelcard Zone 4|4]], (inner suburbs); [[Travelcard Zone 5|5]] and [[Travelcard Zone 6|6]] (outer suburbs)\n\n===Political divisions===\n{{main|List of wards in Greater London|London Assembly constituencies|List of Parliamentary constituencies in Greater London}}\n\n==Geographic features==\n\n===Hills and highest points===\n{| \n{{Location map+|Greater London\n  |caption = \n  |float   = \n  |width   = 350\n  |places = \n{{location map~|Greater London|label=[[Westerham Heights]]|mark=Blue_pog.svg|position=right|background=white|lat=51.289074|long=0.058660|caption=|float=}}\n{{location map~|Greater London|label=[[Sanderstead Plantation]]|position=right|background=white|lat=51.339870 |long=-0.072592|caption=|float=}}\n{{location map~|Greater London|label=[[Bushey Heath|Bushey&nbsp;Heath]]|position=left|background=white|lat=51.630767 |long=-0.336265|caption=|float=}}\n{{location map~|Greater London|label=[[Arkley]]|position=left|background=white|lat=51.646432|long=-0.238850|caption=|float=}}\n{{location map~|Greater London|label=[[Clockhouse Recreation Ground|Clockhouse]]|position=left|background=white|lat=51.323303|long= -0.160836|caption=|float=}}\n{{location map~|Greater London|label=[[Moat Mount Open Space and Mote End Farm|Moat Mount]]|position=right|background=