aftesbury Avenue]]\n* [[Sloane Square]]\n* [[Sloane Street]]\n* [[Strand, London|The Strand]]\n* [[Threadneedle Street]]\n* [[Tottenham Court Road]]\n* [[Trafalgar Square]]\n* [[Victoria Embankment]]\n* [[Wardour Street]]\n* [[Whitehall]]\n}}\n\n===Ruins===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n*[[Barking Abbey]]\n*[[London Wall]]\n*[[Lesnes Abbey]]\n}}\n\n===Shopping arcades===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[Burlington Arcade]]\n* [[Piccadilly Arcade]]\n}}\n\n===Sporting venues===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[All England Lawn Tennis and Croquet Club]] (Wimbledon)\n* [[Boleyn Ground]] (Upton Park)\n* [[Craven Cottage]]\n* [[The Den]]\n* [[Emirates Stadium]]\n* [[Herne Hill Velodrome]]\n* [[Lord's Cricket Ground]]\n* [[Olympic Stadium (London)|Olympic Stadium]]\n* [[The Oval]]\n* [[Selhurst Park]]\n* [[Stamford Bridge (stadium)|Stamford Bridge]]\n* [[Twickenham Stadium]]\n* [[The Valley (London)|The Valley]]\n* [[Vicarage Road]]\n* [[Wembley Stadium]]\n* [[White Hart Lane]]\n}}\n\n===Theatres and concert halls===\n{{main|List of London venues|West End theatre}}\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[Royal Albert Hall|Albert Hall]]\n* [[Alexandra Palace]]\n* [[Royal National Theatre]]\n* [[Royal Festival Hall]]\n* [[South Bank Centre]]\n}}\n\n===Tourist attractions===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[The London Bridge Experience]]\n* [[London Dungeon]]\n* [[London Eye]]\n}}\n\n====Former tourist attractions====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n*[[Millennium Dome]]\n*[[The Crystal Palace]]\n*[[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Pre-2000 Wembley Stadium]]\n}}\n\n===Windmills===\n{{main|List of windmills in Greater London}}\n{{columns-list|colwidth=18em|\n* [[Ashby's Mill]]\n* [[Barnet Gate Mill]]\n* [[Keston Windmill]]\n* [[Plumstead Common Windmill]]\n* [[Shirley Windmill]]\n* [[Upminster Windmill]]\n* [[Wandsworth Common Windmill]]\n* [[Wimbledon Windmill]]\n}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of garden squares in London]]\n* [[List of places in England]]\n* [[:Category:Geography o