ull City A.F.C.|Hull City]]\n|[[2016\u201317 Hull City A.F.C. season|2016\u201317]]\n|[[Premier League]]\n|15||0||0||0||colspan=2|\u2014||0||0||15||0\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 Hull City A.F.C. season|2017\u201318]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[EFL Championship|Championship]]\n|37||9||1||0||colspan=2|\u2014||0||0||38||9\n|-\n|[[2018\u201319 Hull City A.F.C. season|2018\u201319]]\n|38||9||1||0||colspan=2|\u2014||0||0||39||9\n|-\n|[[2019\u201320 Hull City A.F.C. season|2019\u201320]]\n|27||6||2||1||colspan=2|\u2014||0||0||29||7\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total!!118!!24!!4!!1!!colspan=2|\u2014!!0!!0!!122!!25\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total!!389!!71!!36!!6!!2!!0!!11!!1!!438!!78\n|}\n<span id=\"notes gs1\"></span><sup>1</sup><small> Including [[Polish SuperCup]], [[Ekstraklasa Cup]] and [[Coupe de la Ligue]].</small>\n\n===International===\n{{updated|match played 20 November 2019.}}<ref name=\"Stats\"/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align: center\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n! National team||Year||Apps||Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=12|[[Poland national football team|Poland]]\n|2008||2||0\n|-\n|2009||1||0\n|-\n|2010||3||0\n|-\n|2011||4||0\n|-\n|2012||9||0\n|-\n|2013||3||0\n|-\n|2014||5||2\n|-\n|2015||8||4\n|-\n|2016||13||3\n|-\n|2017||7||2\n|-\n|2018||9||1\n|-\n|2019||9||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total||73||13\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''Scores and results list Poland's goal tally first.''<ref>{{cite web|title=Kamil Grosicki|url=http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=26137|publisher=European Football|accessdate=10 September 2014}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! No. !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1.\n| rowspan=2 | 7 September 2014 || rowspan=2 | [[Est\u00e1dio do Algarve]], [[Faro, Portugal|Faro]], [[Portugal]] || rowspan=4 | {{fb|GIB}} || <center>'''1'''\u20130</center> || rowspan=2 | <center>7\u20130</center> || rowspan=4 | [[UEFA Euro 2016 qualifying Group D|UEFA Euro 2016 qualification]]\n|-\n| 2. || <cente